OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FVictims say they are scared for their
OL,7,Fsafety ahead of the release of a
OL,8,Fnotorious grooming gang leader.
OL,10,FShabir Ahmed, 73, went by the nickname
OL,11,F"Daddy" as he plied his underaged
OL,12,Fvictims with drugs and alcohol before
OL,13,Fthey were gang-raped by members of a
OL,14,Fgrooming gang in Rochdale.
OL,16,FAhmed will be freed on Thursday 2 July
OL,17,Fafter serving 14 years in jail since
OL,18,Fhis conviction in 2012 for multiple
OL,19,Frape and sexual offences against young
OL,20,Fgirls.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FSince his conviction there have been
OL,7,Fcalls to deport Ahmed, who holds dual
OL,8,FPakistani-British citizenship, but his
OL,9,Fvictims have now been told he will
OL,10,Fremain in the UK.
OL,12,FOne victim, identified only as "Ruby",
OL,13,Fis being supported by The Maggie
OL,14,FOliver Foundation, set up by Ms
OL,15,FOliver, an ex-police detective-turned-
OL,16,Fwhistleblower over grooming gangs.
OL,18,FRuby said: "I'm scared for my safety
OL,19,Fand my kids' safety.
OL,26,@tD@`OUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,F"The main ringleader is getting out of
OL,7,Fprison, who is well known in Rochdale,
OL,8,FOldham and Middleton, so even if he's
OL,9,Fnot in that area, he still knows
OL,10,Fpeople and has a chance to talk to
OL,11,Fpeople from that area and that makes
OL,12,Fme unsafe."
OL,14,FRuby added that victims of abuse had
OL,15,Fbeen given "false promises" and left
OL,16,Fto "fend for themselves" through a
OL,17,Flack of support from the authorities
OL,18,Fand called for a change in the law to
OL,19,Fget grooming gang members deported.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FAnother victim said she will be
OL,7,F"unable to live freely or safely"
OL,8,Fwhile Ahmed remains free.
OL,10,FThrough the organisation Parents
OL,11,FAgainst Grooming UK, she said: "The
OL,12,Fpending release of Shabir Ahmed from
OL,13,Fprison has had a profound and
OL,14,Fdebilitating impact on my life.
OL,16,F"I live in a constant state of
OL,17,Fhypervigilance, fearing for my
OL,18,Fphysical safety every time I leave my
OL,19,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,F"This fear has caused severe anxiety,
OL,7,Fdisrupted my sleep, and forced me to
OL,8,Fdrastically alter my daily routines,
OL,9,Fand social life simply to avoid a
OL,10,Fpotential confrontation."
OL,12,FDocuments published online, apparently
OL,13,Ffrom the Probation Service, to one of
OL,14,FAhmed's victims, states he will be
OL,15,Freleased on 2 July and cannot be
OL,16,Fdeported back to Pakistan due to
OL,17,Fprovisions in the Immigration Act 1971
OL,18,Fwhich bar his removal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FThese are that he arrived in the UK
OL,7,Fbefore 1973 and had lived in the UK
OL,8,Ffor at least five years before his
OL,9,Fdeportation was considered.
OL,11,FThe failure to deport multiple men
OL,12,Fwith dual nationality convicted of
OL,13,Fserious child sex offences in grooming
OL,14,Fgangs has caused deep anger in many
OL,15,Fcommunities and heaped pressure on
OL,16,Fpoliticians.
OL,18,FA national inquiry into grooming gangs
OL,19,Fwas announced earlier this year after
OL,20,Fthe Government came under increasing
OL,21,Fcriticism.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FIn 2022, Andy Burnham, then the mayor
OL,7,Fof Greater Manchester and now likely
OL,8,Fto replace Sir Keir Starmer as the
OL,9,Fnext Prime Minister, called on the
OL,10,Fthen Conservative government "to do
OL,11,Feverything within... the government's
OL,12,Fpower" to deport grooming gang members.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FAhmed is reportedly being held at HMP
OL,7,FLeeds and it is understood he will be
OL,8,Freleased on licence with terms that he
OL,9,Fmust initially live at accommodation
OL,10,Fwhich is staffed 24 hours, so he
OL,11,Fcannot return to his last known
OL,12,Faddress on Windsor Avenue in Oldham
OL,13,Fand is subject to an "exclusion zone"
OL,14,Fcentred on Rochdale.
OL,16,FFor two years from early 2008, girls
OL,17,Fas young as 12 were plied with alcohol
OL,18,Fand drugs, gang-raped in rooms above
OL,19,Ftakeaway shops and ferried to
OL,20,Fdifferent flats in taxis where cash
OL,21,Fwas paid to use the girls for sex.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FAhmed had worked as a taxi driver but
OL,7,Fwas also employed by Oldham Council as
OL,8,Fa benefits rights worker and seconded
OL,9,Fto the Oldham Pakistani Community
OL,10,FCentre.
OL,12,FAt his trial, Ahmed called the judge a
OL,13,F"racist b******" and took his case to
OL,14,Fthe European Court of Human Rights,
OL,15,Fclaiming he did not get a fair trial.
OL,17,FHe was jailed for 19 years in 2012 at
OL,18,FLiverpool Crown Court, one of nine men
OL,19,Fin the Rochdale grooming gang trial
OL,20,Fconvicted of offences against five
OL,21,Fgirls.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FPolice said the victims were from
OL,7,F"chaotic", "council estate"
OL,8,Fbackgrounds and as many as 50 girls
OL,9,Fcould have been victims of the gang.
OL,11,FJudge Gerald Clifton said victims were
OL,12,Ftreated "as though they were worthless
OL,13,Fand beyond any respect" because they
OL,14,Fwere not part of the gang's community
OL,15,For religion.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police said at the
OL,18,Ftime there was no "racial or cultural"
OL,19,Felement to the crimes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FA report later found that police did
OL,7,Fnot act despite multiple concerns
OL,8,Fbeing raised, citing "serious multiple
OL,9,Ffailures" by officers and local
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FAhmed's case follows a similar legal
OL,13,Fbattle by two other gang members, Qari
OL,14,FAbdul Rauf and Adil Khan.
OL,16,FBoth were stripped of their British
OL,17,Fcitizenship in 2022, 10 years after
OL,18,Ftheir convictions, after fighting a
OL,19,Flong legal battle which went all the
OL,20,Fway to the Court of Appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,FBoth invoked their human rights under
OL,7,Farticle eight of the European
OL,8,FConvention on Human Right - the right
OL,9,Fto a private and family life, to avoid
OL,10,Fdeportation.
OL,12,FThe Home Office has not said if either
OL,13,Fhave been deported.
OL,15,FA spokeswoman for the Home Office said
OL,16,Fon Tuesday: "Our thoughts are first
OL,17,Fand foremost with the victims of these
OL,18,Fappalling crimes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782928087
OL,3,CVictims terrified ahead of release of
OL,4,Cgrooming gang ringleader 'Daddy'
OL,6,F"On his release he will be on the sex
OL,7,Foffenders register for life, ordered
OL,8,Fto stay away from his victims and
OL,9,Fbanned from contacting any child or
OL,10,Fyoung person.
OL,12,F"As well as facing strict curfews and
OL,13,Frestriction zones, his every movement
OL,14,Fwill be tracked, forced to wear an
OL,15,Felectronic tag. Should he breach his
OL,16,Fconditions, he will be immediately
OL,17,Flocked up."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
